Stage 4 is the last state of tuning for most cars. Whatâ€™s modified for a tune to be classed as stage 4 is open to interpretation  but at the very least  it is here that an upgraded turbocharger/ supercharger  such as a hybrid turbo  is installed. Along with that  most tuning companies will also install a re-circulating dump valve and enlarged  ported wastegate.Stage 4 may also include an upgraded oil cooler  multi-hole injectors  bearing assembly.
